#
# https://spring.io/guides/gs/rest-service/
# 
# my clone of project is in https://github.com/oleg-duvanayev/spring.boot.rest.github.git
#

1. start the application with:
~> git spring-boot:run
2. point the browser to
http:localhost:8080/greeting


#
# you can request the service from CLI as well:
#
~> curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/?name=Oleg | python -m json.tool
